title: Black Sesame Banana Bread Recipe from El Rey | Sweet Spots
description:
Bon Appétit’s Alison Roman pays a visit to El Rey Coffee Shop to learn how to make chef Gerardo Gonzalez’s sweet and savory black sesame banana bread. Learn his tricks to upping your banana bread game at home.
